data.description: The definition of turn-key! This updated ranch home in Earl Lake Heights includes deeded lake access, so all you have to do is move in. Perfect location in a quiet neighborhood close to downtown Howell. All new flooring and fresh paint in the home, kitchen has granite counters, new fixtures, newer cabinets, wood floors, stainless appliances. Family room has sliding door to back patio plus a natural stone fireplace. Full bath with double sinks on the main floor, plus three bedrooms. Basement is the perfect space to spread out, with open entertaining space plus storage, laundry room with new washer and dryer, and rooms for office, crafts, or play area. On just under a half acre, the fenced yard has room to play and keeps that neighborhood feel. Deeded access to all-sports Earl Lake is at the end of the street with a large beach area, dock and launch for residents to use. New water heater, furnace 3 yrs old, new electrical panel, Kinetico water softener, new exterior shake and new gutters and soffits. Check it out today!
